  - Discernment-Truth=The Eye Of Eternity-Supreme Center=Resolution of Contraries
By: Ibn al-'Arif
---
His life (is) without death, his knowledge without ignorance, his will
without aversion, his power without impotence, his hearing without deafness,
his vision without blindness, his speech without aphonia, nor are any of
his faculties ever annihilated by their contraries.
